import React from "react";

const SvgLogo = props => (
  <svg width={42} height={43} {...props}>
    <defs>
      <pattern
        id="logo_svg__a"
        preserveAspectRatio="none"
        width="100%"
        height="100%"
        viewBox="0 0 621 626"
      >
        <image
          width={621}
          height={626}
          xlinkHref="data:image/png;base64,"
        />
      </pattern>
    </defs>
    <path
      data-name="9c19ad762cbdb27439cd4455ec7f33e7"
      fill="url(#logo_svg__a)"
      d="M0 0h42v43H0z"
    />
  </svg>
);

export default SvgLogo;
